title: I'll Name This Podcast Later Episode 54
description: The return of Rosenberg, in Joe's absence, Mari and Rory sit with Peter Rosenberg to discuss Mari's Toronto disappearance, The Grammy's, Karen Civil, Peter's gig at ESPN, and the overall direction of the Podcast. Sleeper songs of the week: Marisa's pick: MGK ft.
